        "created_at": "2020-02-09T23:53:33.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>At TJ\u2019s for $6.99<br>\nThis is very bright, zingy, acidity-driven, minerals, tannins\u2026cherry/raspberry enriched sunshine\u2026an always interesting sip/gulp. A solid, satisfying, medium finish.<br>\nAt this price, I\u2019ve bought multiple cases. Given it\u2019s relative structure, this has some agability to it, to boot.</p>",
