        "created_at": "2020-02-10T16:43:48.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"158325\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Which bottling was this?  He has a bunch.</p>\n<p>FWIW I noticed Total Wine sells a lot of bojo bottles that look almost exactly the same (flowers etc) but the producer is Debeaune or someone.  Caveat Emptor !</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Jean-Claude Debeaune is a variant label that Duboeuf produces specially for Total Wine, so the resemblance is not coincidental.</p>",
