        "created_at": "2021-07-13T00:33:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Opened up another bottle of this, 17 months after my last note. Drinking from a Grassl Libertine glass. This is STILL drinking SO well as no-brain-needed wine enjoyment\u2026 snappy red fruits, and high-toned acid thrown into mix for FUN.<br>\nI\u2019m sorry that Todd French didn\u2019t care for this. It\u2019s NOT a wine of significance, just tasty for $7.</p>",
